
Simple Calculator is very early stage of Calculator program.
Objective is to learn iOS platform and make something useful.

== Development Platform  ==
* Xcode 4.3.2
* iOS 5.1


== Known Issues ==
* Does not handle decimal places.
* Limited to basic operations like plus, minus, multiply devide.
* There is no Memory Store or Recall.
* It is not designed to handle multiple orientation of device.

== More Details ==
* Step by Step guide can be found here : 
** http://deepakkeswani.com/2012/02/writing-calculator-for-iphone-ios-in-xcode/